I refer to your email of 8 July 2006 in which you claim >www.globalcloning.com is no longer contactable. I advise that the site is still contactable on an IP address registered to your company. We ask that you act expeditiously to remove or disable access to the material or items claimed to be infringing as per the original DMCA notice below. Should you fail to do so we will consider that your company is in support of this breach of our copyright materials in this matter and may seek legal redress through the courts.

You assistance in advance is thanked.

Sincerely
Duncan Riley.
